title: Chiefs WR Worthy won't be charged after arrest
description: The Williamson County district attorney's office has declined to press charges against Chiefs receiver Xavier Worthy following his arrest for an alleged assault.

title: Source: Ravens to re-sign Stanley to 3-year deal
description: The Baltimore Ravens will re-sign veteran left tackle Ronnie Stanley, 30, a two-time Pro Bowl player who has been the franchise's starting left tackle since 2016, to a three-year, $60 million deal, a source told ESPN's Adam Schefter on Saturday.
author: Jamison Hensley

title: 'The first of three finals' - how good can Liverpool's season be?
description: Liverpool's dream of achieving the Treble was ended last month by Plymouth in the fourth round of the FA Cup - but they remain firmly in the hunt for three trophies.

title: 'Free-scoring French leave Irish history tilt in tatters'
description: Ireland hosted France in the Aviva Stadium seeking to make history. Instead a signature achievement has slipped from their grasp for the third time in 17 months.

title: New ban for Millwall goalkeeper Roberts after Mateta challenge
description: Millwall goalkeeper Liam Roberts has been handed a six-match ban for his challenge on Jean-Philippe Mateta which hospitalised the Crystal Palace forward.
